\c 30
\s Ukubonga kosilisiweyo ekufeni
\d Isihlabelelo. Ingoma yokwehlukaniswa kwendlu kaDavida
\p
\v 1 Ngizakuphakamisa, N\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba ungenyusile\x + Hlab. 107.32.\x*, njalo kawuthokozisanga izitha zami ngami\x + Hlab. 35.19,24. Hlab. 13.4.\x*.
\v 2 N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wami, ngakhalela kuwe\x + Hlab. 88.13.\x*, wangisilisa\x + Hlab. 6.2.\x*.
\v 3 N\nd kosi\nd*, uwukhuphulile umphefumulo wami\x + Hlab. 86.13.\x* engcwabeni\x + Hlab. 16.10.\x*, ungigcinile ngiphila, ukuze ngingehleli emgodini\x + Hlab. 28.1.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Hlabelelani eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lina bangcwele bayo\x + Hlab. 50.5.\x*, libonge ekukhunjulweni kobungcwele bayo.
\v 5 Ngoba ukuthukuthela kwayo kungokwesikhatshana\x + Isa. 26.20.54.7,8. Hlab. 103.9.\x*, impilo isemuseni wayo\x + Hlab. 63.3.\x*. Ukulila kungahlala kusihlwa\x + 2 Kor. 4.17.\x*, kanti ekuseni kulentokozo\x + Hlab. 5.3.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Mina-ke ngathi ekuphumeleleni kwami\x + Jobe 29.18.\x*: Kangiyikunyikinywa laphakade\x + Hlab. 10.6.\x*.
\v 7 N\nd kosi\nd*, ngomusa wakho wenzile intaba yami iqine; wabufihla ubuso bakho, ngahlupheka\x + Hlab. 104.29. Dute. 31.17.\x*.
\v 8 Ngakhala kuwe, N\nd kosi\nd*; ngancenga eNkosini\x + Hlab. 142.1.\x*.
\v 9 Kulenzuzo bani egazini lami ekutshoneni kwami emgodini? Uthuli luzakudumisa na? Luzatshumayela iqiniso lakho yini\x + Hlab. 6.5.\x*?
\v 10 Zwana, N\nd kosi\nd*, ube lomusa kimi; N\nd kosi\nd*, woba ngumsizi wami\x + Hlab. 27.7.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Uphendule ukukhala kwami kwaba yikusina\x + Jer. 31.4,13. Lilo 5.15. Hlab. 149.3. 150.4.\x*; ukhuphile isaka lami, wangibhincisa intokozo\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*,
\v 12 ukuze udumo \add lwami\add* luhlabele indumiso kuwe, lungathuli; N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wami, ngizakubonga kuze kube nininini.